name: Reeveid
content: Reeveid was a Rodian bounty hunter. Tirog, a fellow bounty hunter, arranged to meet with Reeveid in a cantina. Tirog waited half an hour for Reeveid. Thannik, another bounty hunter, also once arranged to meet with Reeveid in a cantina on business. Thannik waited for about half an hour before Reeveid arrived.
